main event: Two witnesses observed an irregularly shaped, brilliant white object moving rapidly across the sky and then disappearing towards the North.
interesting points: The object was irregular in shape and brilliant white in color., The witnesses watched the object for 2 1/2 minutes., The object moved rapidly, stopped abruptly, and remained stationary for 1 minute., No sound was heard during the observation., The object had no apparent trail and was unaccounted for.
witness description: Two witnesses with no specific identifiers provided.
